            <title>[LU-17360] kernel update [RHEL 9.3 5.14.0-362.13.1.el9_3]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17360</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: use-after-free vulnerability in the smb client component (CVE-2023-5345)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: IGB driver inadequate buffer size for frames larger than MTU (CVE-2023-45871)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hw amd: Return Address Predictor vulnerability leading to information disclosure (CVE-2023-20569)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: use-after-free in smb2_is_status_io_timeout() (CVE-2023-1192)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


